msgid "Rooftops"
msgstr "Rooftops"

msgctxt "56_Amateur Skygazer"
msgid ""
"Rooftops must exist so you can get a better look at the sky. I mean, you get"
" your run-of-the-mill weirdos up there, too, but they almost add to the "
"wonder of rooftop skygazing."
msgstr ""
"Rooftops must exist so you can get a better look at the sky. I mean, you get"
" your run-of-the-mill weirdos up there, too, but they almost add to the "
"wonder of rooftop skygazing."

msgctxt "68_Amateur Skygazer"
msgid ""
"You can get to the rooftop areas from various places in Kamurocho. The "
"rooftops are divided into the Southwest and Southeast areas. These areas can"
" be used as alternate routes to typical street routes. Rooftop entrances and"
" exits are marked on your map."
msgstr ""
"You can get to the rooftop areas from various places in Kamurocho. The "
"rooftops are divided into the Southwest and Southeast areas. These areas can"
" be used as alternate routes to typical street routes. Rooftop entrances and"
" exits are marked on your map."

msgctxt "80_Amateur Skygazer"
msgid ""
"However, most building managers deem it too dangerous when it's raining and "
"will close off rooftop entrances in wet weather."
msgstr ""
"However, most building managers deem it too dangerous when it's raining and "
"will close off rooftop entrances in wet weather."

