msgctxt "104_Amateur Skygazer"
msgid ""
"You should learn all the rooftop routes! Not only do you get a killer view "
"of the sky and the city, but you can get to all sorts of unexpected places "
"from way up high!"
msgstr ""
"You should learn all the rooftop routes! Not only do you get a killer view "
"of the sky and the city, but you can get to all sorts of unexpected places "
